  "description": "Hawking radiation is thermal radiation predicted to be emitted by [black holes](./black-hole.md) due to quantum effects near the [event horizon](./event-horizon.md). Stephen Hawking derived this result in 1974-1975, showing that black holes are not perfectly black.",
